                        <span class="font-bold text-sm">Kerala DHS Guidelines</span>
                        <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-auto text-slate-400 group-hover:text-blue-500" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 6H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2v-4M14 4h6m0 0v6m0-6L10 14" /></svg>
